# 🛒 Flipkart Clone

A simple Flipkart-inspired e-commerce webpage built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project was created to practice front-end web development concepts and improve UI design skills.

## 🚀 Live Demo
https://cse-16-236-w18r.vercel.app/

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## ✨ Features
- Responsive Design
- Navigation Bar
- Product Cards & Categories
- Interactive UI Elements
- Clean and User-Friendly Layout

## 👩‍💻 Author
Anshita Garg

## 📌 Purpose
This project was built for learning and practicing front-end web development using basic web technologies without any frameworks.
